text: On Mar. 3, head of the Phase III clinical trial of #Turkey's #COVID19 #vaccine Serhat Unal said that the #CoronaVac vaccine produced by #China's Sinovac Biotech has prevented hospitalization and serious illness in 100% of the cases.
